<% provide :headeractiveclass, "home" %>
<div class="container-fluid after-navbar">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row row-content without-padd">
           <div class="col-xs-12 without-padd">
                <div id="mycarousel" class="hidden-xs carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
                    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                        <li data-target="#mycarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                        <li data-target="#mycarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                    </ol>
                    <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
                    <div class="item active">
                    	<%= image_tag("bg3.jpg", class: "img-responsive") %>
                        <div class="carousel-caption bg3">
                            <a class="btn btn-danger btn-lg" href="/calendar">Race Calender</a><br>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item">
                        <%= image_tag("bg4.jpg", class: "img-responsive") %>
                        <div class="carousel-caption bg4">
                            <a class="btn btn-danger btn-lg" href="/register">Register Now</a><br>
                        </div>
                    </div>                    
                    </div>
                    <a class="left carousel-control" href="#mycarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                    </a>
                    <a class="right carousel-control" href="#mycarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
                        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <%= image_tag("bg4.jpg", class: "img-responsive visible-xs") %>
                <div class="carousel-caption visible-xs bg4">
                    <a class="btn btn-danger btn-sm" href="/register">Register Now</a><br>
                </div>
                
            </div>
        </div> 
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row row-content">
            <div class ="col-xs-12">
                <h1>About us </h1>
                A constant fight in the mind to reach your goal. ‘Shut up legs’ was devised to spread the racing culture amongst passionate cyclists in Mysore. A series of races will be held throughout the year which will include both road biking and mountain biking. For the novices, here’s a perfect exposure to racing. If you are from Mysore, grab this opportunity to explore your own city. If you are not, all the more reason to come visit. So what are you waiting for? Get your bums on the saddle and embark upon this journey through the undulations, curves and paved roads.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<p style="padding:15px;"></p>